The Club offers a variety of membership opportunities, including local, non-local, international and corporate golf as well as social membership. /Grey Card Content Block Golf Membership Golfing members enjoy unrestricted access to all Club amenities, including our championship golf course, practice facilities, full-service Professional Shop and The Workshop, our fully equipped performance center. Designed by premier golf architect Tom Fazio and ranked as one of the top 100 golf courses in the world, Lake Nona’s 18-hole championship golf course is favored by countless professional golfers and world-class athletes who call Lake Nona home. The Workshop at Lake Nona, is one of the most outfitted facilities of its kind in the country and is designed to provide members a comprehensive training experience for players of all levels. Social Membership Social members enjoy a wealth of non-golf amenities, including a variety of dining options, a full calendar of social events, 7,000-square-foot Bath & Racquet Club comprised of state-of-the-art tennis and pickleball courts, all-inclusive Fitness Center with complimentary group fitness classes, Nona Crewhouse, our signature youth activity center, along with a lakeside pool and children’s playground. The 18-room, on-site Lodge offers visiting Members and their guests a home away from home with spacious accommodations overlooking lake and golf course views. The amenities and services extend beyond the Club community with preferred rates and benefits, exclusive to Lake Nona Members, available at the Lake Nona Performance Club, Lake Nona Wave Hotel, and complimentary airport transfers. A vibrant, international population of members and residents enjoy an active lifestyle comprised of wellness, education, recreation and entertainment offerings. /Grey Card Content Block Platinum Club® of the World and Platinum Club® of America Lake Nona Golf & Country Club’s continual pursuit of elevating the member experience and setting a new standard of excellence in service, has propelled the Club to be recognized as both a Platinum Club ® of the World (ranked #40, 2022-2023) and Platinum Club ® of America (ranked #32, 2021-2022) by Club Leaders Forum , one of the most respected sources for club industry leaders and professionals. Platinum Club ® of the World status is the pinnacle of recognition in the private club industry, representing clubs who excel in best practices and set the standard of excellence for the finest private golf and country clubs around the world, as determined by a panel of private club industry experts and golf connoisseurs. Platinum Club ® of America status represents the upper 5% of America’s Top Private Clubs of Excellence, as voted by over 3,000 industry professionals (club general managers, owners and presidents). Conducted every two years, these designations use similar criteria to establish the benchmark of excellence: universal recognition, amenities and facilities, professional services levels, overall experience, governance and management, and adapting to changing times. Distinguished Club™ Elite For seven consecutive years, Boardroom magazine, one of the most respected trade publications serving private clubs, designated Lake Nona Golf & Country Club a Distinguished Club™ Elite through their annual award program. This prestigious designation is awarded to clubs that successfully provide a “world-class member experience”, measured by an extensive evaluation process, including: staff demonstrates super training and service, provides refined facilities, and is recognized in the top echelon of local and regional reputation. Most importantly, the award is presented to clubs that go above and beyond, creating lasting memories that make every experience exceptional. Earning this distinguished title reinforces Lake Nona Golf & Country Club’s ceaseless drive to elevate the member experience. With easy access to the city’s main roadways, Lake Nona is only minutes from dining, nightlife and attractions and less than an hour from the Atlantic coast beaches. For international residents, the community is a convenient 10-minute drive from Orlando International Airport. Recognizing that each event is unique, our team will graciously accommodate your personalized needs, crafting a one-of-a-kind event that is seamless from beginning to end. From picturesque weddings and milestone celebrations, to luncheons, business dinners and corporate galas, our experienced catering professionals will expertly lead the planning services with great attention to detail, while our award-winning chefs create diverse menus, delivering inspired cuisine to please every palate. Champagne toasts, pre-wedding planning and vendor selection are just a few of the services offered through our comprehensive bridal packages, while our team of experienced professionals deliver inspired cuisine, impeccable service and a seamless experience to ensure your big day is truly momentous.
